  description: "When you perform a Strong Gambit with a\nbladed weapon you may choose
    one of the\nfollowing as the effect, the target receiving a\nSave as normal:\n\u2022
    Take a limb\n\u2022 Take a head if their GD is 0\nPASSION - Diligence\nRestore
    SPI when refusing a shortcut.\nAs sword abend, as plate afold,\nAs shield asplint,
    a tale atold.\nIron Knight\nORIGIN OF THE CLEAVINGBLADE\nOut of a... At a time
    of...\n1 Vibrant forest Contentment\n2 High waterfall Desperation\n3 Roaring
    sea Victory\n4 Broken boulder Anger\n5 Narrow cave Sorrow\n6 Dead tree Transition\nKNIGHTED
    BY...\nThe Celebrated Seer\nVIG 12, CLA 6, SPI 15, 2 GD\n\u2022 Clad in a coat
    of shining metal masks,\neach an expression of joy.\n\u2022 Only sees moments
    of intense positive\nemotion, more intensity granting clearer\nvisions and pleasure.\n\u2022
    Wants praise and elaborate celebrations,\nnot really caring what for.\nPerson:
    Hardened scavenger ~ Name: Ellery ~ Characteristic: Head in the clouds\nObject:
    Creation chest ~ Beast: Tiger spider ~ State: Celebrating ~ Theme: Fungi\n4\n8\nThe"
